		<SimpleData name="Descriptio">From the Village Square follow the route across the Tallaght Bypass, and onto the Old Bawn Road. Turn right onto Firhouse Road West and then right again onto Whitestown Way. At the T-junction, turn right onto the Tallaght Bypass and continue back to the</SimpleData>
