		<SimpleData name="Descriptio">From the Library on Monastery Road, the 3.8 Km circuit of Clondalkin follows the road past the Old Monastery Wall to the roundabout at the top of Woodford. This is the highest point in Clondalkin and on a clear day you have a great view of Dublin Bay and</SimpleData>
