		<SimpleData name="BuggyWheel">No</SimpleData>
		<SimpleData name="NearestTow">Tallaght</SimpleData>
		<SimpleData name="ExternalLi"></SimpleData>
		<SimpleData name="Descriptio">This Slí na Slainte trail on the slopes of Cruagh Mountain has a hard core surface throughout. It offers panoramic views of the Tibradden, Two Rock, Three Rock and Glendoo Mountains as well as Dun Laoghaire Harbour and Howth with Dublin spread at your f</SimpleData>
		<SimpleData name="Starting_P">Cruagh Car Park</SimpleData>
