		<SimpleData name="Descriptio">The Saggart-Rathcoole Slí na Sláinte, a 4 km route which begins at “Teacht Sagart”, Saggart Heritage &amp; Arts Centre, on Garters Lane. The route continues up Garters Lane towards the village and past the beautiful 19th century Parish Church on the le</SimpleData>
